      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 underline">About Me</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
          Dharmik Jadav - Software Engineer
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col mb-3">
          <p class="">
            I am Dharmik Jadav, a software engineer with a background in IT.
          </p>
          <p>I'm very passionate for building products.</p>
        </div>
        <p>
          Feel free to reach out if you want to discuss potential
          collaborations, projects, or just to connect!
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 my-4 items-center">
          <a href="https://github.com/dhrmkj">
            <Github height="24px" width="24px" />
          </a>
          <!-- <a>
            <Mail />
          </a> -->
          <a href="https://discord.com/users/1103331985239322635">
            <Discord height="24px" width="24px" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://x.com/dhrmkj">
            <X height="24px" width="24px" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/dhrmkj">
            <Insta height="24px" width="24px" />
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:dhrmkjdv@gmail.com">
            <Mail height="24px" width="24px" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="my-10">
          <h2 class="mb-2 italic">currently working on...</h2>
          <div un-flex="~ col gap-1 items-start">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="post-title!">
                <a
                  href={"https://portal.gstfy.com"}
                  class="underline text-xl"
                  target="_blank"><b>GSTFY</b></a
                >
              </h3>
              <div class="mb-2 text-3.5">
                <span><b>{"Posted At - "}</b></span>
                <time class="italic">{new Date("April 10, 2024 03:24:00")}</time
