                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/savan-nagariya-93b919233/"
                >Savan Nagariya</a
              > on developing a software portal that enables b2b businesses to generate
              e-invoices efficiently.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a
            class="underline font-semibold italic"
            href="https://blog.dharmik.me">go to my blogs</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
